# Please install the following libraries before running the code(Links to each have been provided in the brackets):

1. Scipy(Ubuntu/Linux Install: This will install all the essential libraries including Scipy, Numpy, MatPlot):
sudo apt-get install python-numpy python-scipy python-matplotlib ipython ipython-notebook python-pandas python-sympy python-nose
(Link: http://www.scipy.org/install.html)
2. PyBrain: a). $ git clone git://github.com/pybrain/pybrain.git pybrain 
            b). $ python setup.py install
            (Link: http://pybrain.org/docs/quickstart/installation.html)
3. MFCC Library: a) $ git clone git://github.com/jameslyons/python_speech_features
                 b) $ python setup.py install
